{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "9f8b7c6d-5e4f-4a3b-9c2d-1e0f9a8b7c6d",
    "name": "Assessment System \u2014 Identity Module",
    "description": "Identity domain endpoints (auth, users, roles, security policies, profile, sessions, system health).\n\n## Run order (top \u2192 bottom)\n1. **System** \u2014 sanity check (no auth)\n2. **Auth (Public)** \u2014 Login (captures token/session_id/user_id + mfa_required flag); Verify MFA (skips if no MFA challenge); Forgot Password\n3. **Identity (Self)** \u2014 read endpoints + harmless self-updates; **My Sessions** captures a non-current `target_session_id` for the tear-down folder\n4. **Security Policies** \u2014 show / update\n5. **Users** \u2014 List (fallback `target_user_id`: first non-self user) \u2192 Create (sets `target_user_id`) \u2192 Show / Invite (sets `invite_token` + `invited_user_email`) / Reset / Deactivate\n6. **Roles** \u2014 List (fallback `role_id` capture: first custom role) \u2192 Create (sets `role_id`) \u2192 Update / Assign / Unassign / Delete. Runs AFTER Users so `target_user_id` is available for Assign/Unassign.\n7. **Invitation Flow** \u2014 Accept Invite (skips unless `invite_token` was set by Invite User)\n8. **Tear-down (Destructive \u2014 runs LAST)** \u2014 Refresh \u2192 Revoke One Session \u2192 Reset Forgotten Password (skips unless `reset_token` set) \u2192 Revoke All Sessions \u2192 Logout\n\nEndpoints that need server-side prep (`Verify MFA`, `Reset Forgotten Password`) call `pm.execution.skipRequest()` when prerequisites are missing, so a clean Newman run is green by default.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "System",
